{"tid":1079993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩雙程證漢疑豪宅區踩線　遊蕩罪成即時入獄","createTime":"2019-03-27T09:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T10:56:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1a20af799202cec5219b31f8b163ea2f9254146d","tid":1079993,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/photo/bkn-20190327170741816-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190327174907\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190327170741816-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190327174907&h=df60d6ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島總區機動部隊警員，本周日(24日)晚9時許，在香港仔淺水灣一帶執行反爆竊巡邏，期間在壽臣山村道，發現兩名男子在豪宅外徘徊形迹可疑，遂上前截查。警方經初步調查後，該兩名俱姓袁(23及24歲)內地男子，涉嫌遊蕩被捕，案件交由西區警區重案組跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n被捕兩名男子今日在東區裁判法院，被裁定各一項「遊蕩」罪名成立，2人各被判監3個月，即時入獄。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/bkn-20190327170741816-0327_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fbkn-20190327170741816-0327_00822_001.html&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5TcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=272703e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/bkn-20190327170741816-0327_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcc78e6c274cd8588e442d647ba8d4c3a16a132a","tid":1079993,"uid":50457,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"輸入專材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d6deba90441849af9a8fbf562994cca93e4885","tid":1079993,"uid":141151,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n豪宅區就即刻入獄"},{"pid":"5408699c94696b5e6df2